default4.3default Ethical reporting on the London Stock Exchange (LSE) needs to be improved. There is a heavy weighting of extractiv
defaulte companies on the LSE, however achievements to address their ability to ‘do harm’ has been slow.  It is important therefore to ensure that the Financial Conduct Authority (FCA) is able to hol
defaultd
default companies to account for their behaviour. Other 
defaults
defaulttock exchange
defaults, like the Hong Kong Exchange
