defaultGiven the poor record of the extractives sector on hu
defaultman rights, UK companies seeking government support (
defaulteither through financing, insurance  or 
default ‘soft’ support from 
defaultUK Trade &amp; 
defaultI
defaultnvestment
default) for extractives projects should be
